# Tests

---

## Auth-T1 Backend RBAC — Register and login endpoints
**Status:** implemented
**Test File:** `backend/src/rbac/api.rs` (inline `#[cfg(test)]`)
**Module:** auth
**Tags:** stack:backend, module:auth
**Depends on:** Auth-D1

### Cases

| ID | Description | Expected |
|----|-------------|----------|
| TC-T1.1 | Register valid user | 201 + JWT + roles=["editor"] |
| TC-T1.2 | Register empty username | 400 |
| TC-T1.3 | Register empty password | 400 |
| TC-T1.4 | Register short password (< 4 chars) | 400 |
| TC-T1.5 | Register duplicate username | 409 |
| TC-T1.6 | Login with correct credentials | 200 + JWT |
| TC-T1.7 | Login with wrong password | 401 |
| TC-T1.8 | Login with nonexistent user | 401 |

---

## Auth-T2 Auth Middleware — Protected routes reject unauthenticated requests
**Status:** implemented
**Test File:** `backend/src/rbac/middleware.rs`, `backend/tests/`
**Module:** auth
**Tags:** stack:backend, module:auth
**Depends on:** Auth-A1

### Cases

| ID | Description | Expected |
|----|-------------|----------|
| TC-T2.1 | Request to `/api/forge/*` without JWT | 401 |
| TC-T2.2 | Request to `/api/forge/*` with valid JWT | 200 |
| TC-T2.3 | Request to `/api/auth/login` without JWT | 200 (public) |

