## Auth-T3 JWT Secret Loading
**Status:** implemented
**Test File:** `backend/src/main.rs` helpers
**Module:** auth
**Tags:** stack:backend, module:auth
**Depends on:** Auth-A1

### Cases

| ID | Description | Expected |
|----|-------------|----------|
| TC-T3.1 | First server start | Generates and saves JWT secret |
| TC-T3.2 | Subsequent start | Reuses existing JWT secret |

---

## Auth-T4 Frontend Auth Guard
**Status:** implemented
**Test File:** `frontend/src/App.vue`, `frontend/src/composables/useAuth.ts`
**Module:** auth
**Tags:** stack:frontend, module:auth
**Depends on:** Auth-D1

### Cases

| ID | Description | Expected |
|----|-------------|----------|
| TC-T4.1 | No stored token | Shows LoginView |
| TC-T4.2 | Valid stored token | Shows main app |
| TC-T4.3 | Login with admin/admin | Stores JWT, shows main app |
| TC-T4.4 | Click logout | Clears token, shows LoginView |
| TC-T4.5 | 401 API response | `authFetch` clears auth state |

