## Auth-T5 Permission Enforcement on Forge/Relay Routes
**Status:** draft
**Test File:** `backend/src/rbac/middleware.rs`, `backend/src/main.rs`
**Module:** auth
**Tags:** stack:backend, module:auth
**Depends on:** Auth-G2

### Cases

| ID | Description | Expected |
|----|-------------|----------|
| TC-T5.1 | User without `forge:write` tries mutate | 403 |
| TC-T5.2 | User with `forge:write` tries mutate | 200 |
| TC-T5.3 | Admin user accesses admin routes | 200 |
